<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Login Activity Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #171a241a;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      border: 1px solid #000a185d;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #000a18;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      max-height: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
       background-color: #d85600;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-block {
      background: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
     <img src="<%= logo %>" alt="<%= site_name %> Logo" class="logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong><%= user.full_name %></strong>,</p>
      
      <p>We detected a login to your <strong><%= site_name %></strong> account. Below are the details of this activity:</p>

      <div class="info-block">
        <p><strong>Email Address:</strong> <%= user.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleString('en-US', { timeZone: 'UTC' }) %> UTC</p>
        <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> <%= ip_address || 'Not provided' %></p>
        <p><strong>Device:</strong> <%= device_info || 'Unknown' %></p>
      </div>

      <p>If this login was made by you, no further action is required.</p>
      <p>However, if you did not initiate this activity, we strongly recommend that you reset your password immediately to secure your account.</p>

      <a href="<%= web_url %>/auth/reset-password" class="btn">Secure My Account</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= site_name %>. All rights reserved. <br />
      Need assistance? Contact us at <%= contact_email %>.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
